{"tid":2513988,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中東籍男生被控8.31半周年暴動罪成 續還押至5月24日判刑","createTime":"2021-05-03T03:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T16:33:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8196bde4c3dce528c374dc7f715259a33cdfafb1","tid":2513988,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:24:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15383&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtVLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=97893d0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15383</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第卅二庭<br />\n#姚勳智法官 #聆取對控罪的回答<br />\n#20200229旺角 #831半週年<br />\n👤鈕 (19)🛑已還押逾14個月🛑<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：暴動<br />\n被告被控於2020年2月29日，在旺角西洋菜南街近豉油街一帶參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n控罪2：襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n被告被控於同日，在奶路臣街近彌敦道交界處襲擊正當執行職務的警員34731。<br />\n=================<br />\n‼️被告正式在庭上承認「暴動」罪，因認罪協議，「襲警」罪會存檔法庭‼️<br />\n=================<br />\n法庭把案件押後至2021年5月24日 10:00 進行判刑，期間被告人需繼續還押看管，法庭會為被告索取背景報告，若控辯雙方希望呈上案例予法庭參考，需於5月17日前呈上法庭。"},{"pid":"55a227026fd5b5a2ee613558d55521c7b1463b05","tid":2513988,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8395780c4c35f7d10b7fd12daffaae80e6f30c9d","tid":2513988,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5d222dd358badb31ef8997d0cf0b9f583da10c","tid":2513988,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TLPWjlx4hf_AHnru4pxxeHaC7Ow=/802x498/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ESAXKCOOXMGV6WFYGMEANXEA2U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTLPWjlx4hf_AHnru4pxxeHaC7Ow%3D%2F802x498%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FESAXKCOOXMGV6WFYGMEANXEA2U.gif&h=108d9f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.31半周年有便衣警落單在旺角遭「私了」，一度拔槍自保，到場增援的防暴警拘捕一名外籍VTC學生，指他向警員投擲水樽和用竹枝指向警員。<br />\n<br />\n控罪書上顯示被告是「中東籍」，他被控於2020月年2月29日在奶路臣街近彌敦道交界襲擊警員A。<br />\n<br />\n被告毋須答辯，本案押後待警方撿取案發現場的閉路電視片段、為目擊證人錄取口供，及索取警員A的醫療報告等。主任裁判官羅德泉拒絕被告保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200303/O4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FO4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtVLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=f2ffd345\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FO4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU%2F&h=598fe943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200303/O4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU/</a>"},{"pid":"be03ab4910a5bc7e74e1ab1888463a4fab29a4c4","tid":2513988,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f204678a8e0f097a35c8d99cb4a39b4a513c3510","tid":2513988,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a98553794e8dec128082da85e9041b60c23a0bf","tid":2513988,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:33:54.000Z","msg":"扔個水樽就暴動，唉"},{"pid":"40e982744150848761025e74c4b6104e8f1d871b","tid":2513988,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f5d222dd358badb31ef8997d0cf0b9f583da10c","tid":2513988,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TLPWjlx4hf_AHnru4pxxeHaC7Ow=/802x498/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ESAXKCOOXMGV6WFYGMEANXEA2U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTLPWjlx4hf_AHnru4pxxeHaC7Ow%3D%2F802x498%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FESAXKCOOXMGV6WFYGMEANXEA2U.gif&h=108d9f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.31半周年有便衣警落單在旺角遭「私了」，一度拔槍自保，到場增援的防暴警拘捕一名外籍VTC學生，指他向警員投擲水樽和用竹枝指向警員。<br />\n<br />\n控罪書上顯示被告是「中東籍」，他被控於2020月年2月29日在奶路臣街近彌敦道交界襲擊警員A。<br />\n<br />\n被告毋須答辯，本案押後待警方撿取案發現場的閉路電視片段、為目擊證人錄取口供，及索取警員A的醫療報告等。主任裁判官羅德泉拒絕被告保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200303/O4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FO4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtVLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=f2ffd345\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FO4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU%2F&h=598fe943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200303/O4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:35:52.000Z","msg":"Full gear 都咁撚淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d697833e026fbcb575e74d2738a9032914556f0","tid":2513988,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:36:49.000Z","msg":"小小事都暴動"},{"pid":"db85cbbbfcd0218e464c1cf4b2e6e2fc3a3bb014","tid":2513988,"uid":314509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"乜嘢叫「中東籍」？邊個國家叫「中東」？<br />\n法律文件都寫到咁含糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f59d0569f125582139a5c1eb48d947be76bfdb","tid":2513988,"uid":254246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a53e080ce2a72402115e64cdceb73e933172c6","tid":2513988,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b35f9ffacc4837017eb582ab59b390ced6d07b","tid":2513988,"uid":84668,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:46:34.000Z","msg":"南亞手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812e5b28b0207d24dbe3ab1aab1929aa1ea28626","tid":2513988,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"好記得呢隻黑狗柒撚懵懵咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a1a33cd374e7e237b816cd2b9e7a9cbb4a43dd","tid":2513988,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:03:32.000Z","msg":"案情指，當日大批示威者於旺角及太子集結，涉案警員遂奉命在兩區巡邏。警員便衣執勤，但穿著標準警察背心。晚上約10時許，警車巡經彌敦道與山東街交界時，目睹約十多名黑衣人在該處架設路障。警員遂與同僚下車追捕，期間有人稱警員掉了一些裝備，警員停下檢查，因而落了單。十多人隨即靠攏及襲擊警員，向其投擲雜物。警員的頭盔在過程中被搶去，更被示威者拳打腳踢至倒地。警員感覺生命安全受到威脅，遂擎槍自衛。<br />\n<br />\n被告期間先後向警員投擲竹支及水樽。警員多次嘗試突圍而出均不成功，及至其他警員到場才成功脫險。被告亦隨後被捕。由豉油街至雅蘭中心，警員至少被示威者追趕了200米。<br />\n<br />\n被告當日約晚上8時獨自到達西洋菜南街與豉油街交界，現場有大批示威者聚集。不久，他聽到有人大叫「唔好畀個警察走！」，並追打該警員。被告順勢加入，向警員投擲竹枝及水樽。警員事後到醫院求醫，醫療報告指其頭部、雙臂及雙腿擦傷腫脹，左腳踝骨折，並獲批23天病假。"},{"pid":"dd291f5f7100161e86ec41d1825b41d8b13cf94a","tid":2513988,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde961cc2c3562505907cb127f46774667d96577","tid":2513988,"uid":45857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:09:02.000Z","msg":"如果量刑48個月左右<br />\n1/3認罪硬食<br />\n1/3獄中表現<br />\n14個月還押<br />\n最快今年8～9月挨完<br />\n<br />\n如果狗官玩野的佢去教導所之類，就有撚排仲要白坐14個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08863d66f7441d78aad458591e4767e33ab4994a","tid":2513988,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:11:18.000Z","msg":"乜有國家叫中東咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b916cf901c97c0676ec7a51dee3181fd3a342c6","tid":2513988,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eef34ae7586e87429e09e9ee6c8a6f62e3b339b","tid":2513988,"uid":62305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:55:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655e2f52a89921704dcb5943ac2ade12ba099668","tid":2513988,"uid":334957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"vtc南亞仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e6d194b6b179974d44721b53d8cf3fd9fde74a","tid":2513988,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:44:56.000Z","msg":"警員34731趁機突圍跑向豉油街，多人追上並投擲水樽和雜物。事件最遲於此階段演變為暴動。被告在人群中，向警員34731扔物。多段片段拍到被告參與暴動。被告追擊警員34731時，跑至近雅蘭中心外彎身拾起一根竹。被告跑前，追至警員34731，在其身後4至5米。被告再拾起另一根竹，一名便衣警察隨即制服被告，其他警員上前去援，拘捕被告。<br />\n<br />\n在警誡下，被告承認知道警員34731為便衣警察，並<span class=\"red\">承認曾向他投擲水樽和竹枝</span>。根據警員34731的醫療報告，警員34731 的頭部、雙臂和雙腿擦傷腫脹，左腳踝骨折（以腳踝支架固定）。警員 34731 獲批共 23 天病假。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86-%E8%90%BD%E5%96%AE%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%AD%A6-%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E7%B1%8D%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%AA%8D%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E8%2590%25BD%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%259D%25B1%25E7%25B1%258D%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtVLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=1dd117b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E8%2590%25BD%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%259D%25B1%25E7%25B1%258D%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4%2F&h=3ffac0b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86-%E8%90%BD%E5%96%AE%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%AD%A6-%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E7%B1%8D%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%AA%8D%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4/</a>"},{"pid":"70bda7e039b5a6c7c885fdba56d13b02a5f0bf64","tid":2513988,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d2e79cacbde43c38d4477ad448c2c6cbb27fcb","tid":2513988,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458a87265364ca26ced87e4019af05dd398428c4","tid":2513988,"uid":388684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bde961cc2c3562505907cb127f46774667d96577","tid":2513988,"uid":45857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:09:02.000Z","msg":"如果量刑48個月左右<br />\n1/3認罪硬食<br />\n1/3獄中表現<br />\n14個月還押<br />\n最快今年8～9月挨完<br />\n<br />\n如果狗官玩野的佢去教導所之類，就有撚排仲要白坐14個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:22:05.000Z","msg":"唔會入教導所，也不會用48月做量刑起點，預5年差唔多。"}]}